name: Codeatsix-ios
body:
### Contributing You're welcome to fork the repository and make a pull-request whenever your feature/fix is ready. To get the app working, clone the repository, and get the Submodules
``` $ cd codeatsix-ios ```
``` $ git submodule init ```
``` $ git submodule update ```
tagline: iOS version of CodeAtSix meetup site
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
